# Reproducible build outputs from scripts/build.sh. The canonical sha256
# is tracked via dist/SHA256SUMS; the wasm bytes themselves are shipped
# to subkube's prebuilts/ rather than committed here.
dist/alkanes.wasm
.verify-a/
.verify-b/

# align-main: native build artifact of the root indexer package. build.rs
# derives its scratch output dir as <repo>/alkanes when the root `alkanes`
# crate is built for the host target (e.g. `cargo check --workspace`). Not
# source (this branch keeps std contracts under crates/alkanes-std-*).
/alkanes/
